    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Bridgeman Downs?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Block size is the primary driver in Bridgeman Downs. The suburb is known for generous lots on quiet tree-lined streets, and homes on 600 to 800 square metre blocks consistently attract strong family buyer demand. Position relative to school catchments and the quality of the home's condition also play a significant role.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Bridgeman Downs?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Bridgeman Downs homes typically sell within 25 to 40 days. The suburb draws a reliable family buyer pool from across the northern corridor, particularly from buyers priced out of Aspley and Carseldine who recognise the value that Bridgeman Downs offers for block size and quiet suburban character.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Bridgeman Downs?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Bridgeman Downs offers a quiet, family-oriented lifestyle with generous blocks, parks and easy access to Westfield Chermside for shopping and dining. It appeals to families who want space and established suburban character without paying inner-ring prices, and who value access to quality schools including Padua College.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Bridgeman Downs a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Bridgeman Downs continues to attract consistent buyer demand from families seeking large blocks at a value point below its northern neighbours. Limited stock turnover and persistent demand from the school-catchment family market have supported steady price levels, and the suburb remains one of the more reliable family addresses on the northern corridor.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

